{"tid":1545014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"玩屎玩曱甴","createTime":"2019-09-05T18:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T18:12:12.000Z","uid":134244,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a560b2a001c890454589235363aa9c3e3bcb94cf","tid":1545014,"uid":134244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:07:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好玩屎 玩曱甴？ <br />\n撚狗有好多其他方法 點解要用啲殺敵一千 自損八百既方法？<br />\n撚狗重要 但係更重要係越來越多同路人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日聽到人話 「宜家都唔醒既人 係叫唔醒 放棄算」<br />\n真心聽到好灰好忟 <br />\n前線戰場固然重要 但係民意都好重要架<br />\n啲狗只係condom 黎架炸 真正boss 係個政權<br />\n你估林奠驚你地玩殘班condom仔多啲 定係越來越多黃絲多啲？<br />\n希望大家做之前諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想同大家一齊贏呢場仗<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"b0d005cbe8630f879ab7389a7e7fdafc8192d6ad","tid":1545014,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:07:37.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03c539155810d7d725a2fcfefe5e0f8c7ac9aa7e","tid":1545014,"uid":134244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:09:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"039449b3d2bf418517b18e8a08406b6f3e5f8d0a","tid":1545014,"uid":134244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e66b56a4c1f7d43da10cf013d67da454224f6491","tid":1545014,"uid":134244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c938e15df7d60e2